A [[exchange|currency_exchange]] site, operated by Mang Sweeney in the Philippines, where bitcoins may be bought or sold.

This service is useful for using bitcoins to send remittance payments to the Philippines.

The price at which the bitcoins are bought or sold is established at the time the order is placed.

Languages: English, Pinoy

##Buying Bitcoins

The options for paying for the Bitcoin purchase are:

* PHP - Cash deposit at a Philippine bank
* PHP - Cash, local trade in metro Manilla
* PHP - Globe GCash sent via mobile
* USD - Via credit card or bank transfer (ACH) to GCash through the [Remitly](http://www.remitly.com) international transfer remittance network.

##Selling Bitcoins

The options for receiving the proceeds from the sale of bitcoins are:

* PHP - Cash deposited into recipient's account at a Philippine bank 
* PHP - Cash, local pickup in metro Manilla
* PHP - Sent to recipient's mobile through Globe GCash

##History

The service was launched June 18, 2012 (4.1).  As of August 11, 2012 this remains the only exchange offering service in the Philippines.

